{
  "stem": "17543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was so much better than in Auschwitz, of course, because at least we had some civilized way toilet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, that was wooden toilets with the little cubicles, so we wasn't seeing each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had some days when we was-- when the weather turned better, I remember we was outside of the building, and I just kept on looking at how people could escape, because I see on one side of the building there was a leak or some water, which [INAUDIBLE] right to the building.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the windows were so small that nobody could get out on that windows, because I see the other side of the-- that water quite a distance away.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's houses, and on-- on that side where I was standing, where the dry land was, I seen-- I only could see above the gates.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I seen mountains and I seen the train go in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I thought how about somebody managed to-- I mean, we had-- we owned nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Somebody could write a big note-- you know, help, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know who was on those trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Would anybody recognize?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were standing on the grounds outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We was waiting for-- for another set of this stripe uniform [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't very good material, because it was fraying out so much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was in Mauthausen that you're talking--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was Mauthausen, yes, and was the very start being good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we wasn't sleeping and wasn't go to work, we could be in the courtyard, but not-- not standing in five by five, like Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could just mingle about.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was just thinking about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, there's people around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they don't know we are here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How could they?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
